Welcome to wxTreeMultiCtrl 
--------------------------
    A wxWidgets control that allows wxWindow controls to be shaped in a tree, 
    with folding capabilities, like a scrollable property sheet.

Information
-----------    Check the site http://www.xs4all.nl/~jorgb/wb    Click on wxWidgets and find wxTreeMultiCtrl for all up to date information. If the 
    site vanished, google for it I am sure it moved it somewhere!
    
    If you can't get it to work, don't hesitate to email me; jorgb@xs4all.nl
